    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and it\u2019s been such a dependable ride for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape, drives super smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s perfect if you want something reliable and ready to hit the road today. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
